abstract: >-
  TPM-MCP provides a local Technical Product Manager MCP Server that allows you to manage your projects and tasks.
  Features include:
  - Tracking projects, tickets, tasks, dependencies, notes, blockers, assignees, acceptance criteria, etc
  - Generating PDF reports of your projects and tasks
  - Local and secure data store
  - Agentic setup for automated project management
